# Wiki and documentation

## Source of truth

- Edit `ARCHITECTURE.md` and `docs/adr/` in the repo.
- Sync to `wiki/` before commit: `Sync-WikiFolder <repo-path>` or `_devkit\sync-wiki-folder.ps1`.
- CI (`sync-wiki.yml`) publishes `wiki/` to GitHub Wiki on merge to `main`.

## Do not

- Edit wiki pages only in the GitHub Wiki UI — automation overwrites them on merge.
- Store secrets or live credentials in wiki markdown.

## After structural changes

Update `ARCHITECTURE.md`, ADRs, run wiki sync, commit `wiki/**` with code changes.
